{"tid":2257532,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"自爆「懷疑周杰倫係哥哥姜大衛私生子」　爾冬陞︰特地查出生日期","createTime":"2020-10-25T08:35:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T09:28:45.000Z","uid":130626,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2f95bd43f6ac61afd9bc8db5e38660819dfbefe5","tid":2257532,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:35:23.000Z","msg":"知名大導、香港電影金像獎協會主席爾冬陞，近日出演內地綜藝節目《演員請就位》第二季，頻頻引起話題。今次繼「爾冬陞年輕時好帥」後，又有「爾冬陞曾懷疑周杰倫是姜大衛私生子」的關鍵句登上微博熱搜榜首！<br />\n<br />\n有網民翻看爾冬陞早年的訪問，他竟然曾講到「自己懷疑過周杰倫是哥哥姜大衛的私生子」，更有特意查了周杰倫的資料！<br />\n<br />\n早前內地網民對於爾冬陞、秦沛和姜大衛為同母異父的親兄弟已感到大為出奇，因為媽媽當年再婚嫁人，誕下爾冬陞。兩位哥哥都是演員，爾冬陞同樣因為出眾的外形和演技，一躍成為男主角，紅極一時。<br />\n<br />\n在當年的訪問中，爾冬陞表示自己非常真摯地懷疑過︰「究竟周杰倫是不是姜大衛的私生子」，他自言在第一次見到周杰倫後，感到非常震驚，因為周杰倫像極了姜大衛年輕的時候。<br />\n<br />\n爾冬陞：「他完全就是我哥年輕時啊，我還特地查了下他的出生年月，往前倒10個月，我哥還真在台灣！」<br />\n<br />\n事實上，姜大衛跟周杰倫相差32歲，的確生得出周杰倫！另外，周杰倫在2013年自導自編自演的電影《天台》中，周杰倫找來姜大衛來演他的老年，原來是因為周杰倫跟劉偉強等香港導演合作時，曾聽說自己跟後生時期的姜大衛很相似，及後再上網翻查資料，才知道大前輩的厲害，冒昧請姜大衛來客串，周杰倫都笑指自己有點不好意思。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201024/396691240738885632694781.jpeg/GySToKkkQKEY6bRd0qzWUj_fONvS4bKDfFXQ4HxV0OA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201024%2F396691240738885632694781.jpeg%2FGySToKkkQKEY6bRd0qzWUj_fONvS4bKDfFXQ4HxV0OA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=3b397154&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201024/396691243112992768865031.jpeg/qaTtlDNWM8m50e0pKhpnz0lolg_H_QrZIU3H4CFNx-A?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201024%2F396691243112992768865031.jpeg%2FqaTtlDNWM8m50e0pKhpnz0lolg_H_QrZIU3H4CFNx-A%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=4606f253&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a3d882d72f6ab5b1d6e4416c2035268c5a08207","tid":2257532,"uid":87573,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:38:32.000Z","msg":"再鋒利既刀都有生銹既一日....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a0a5a3a5d28607714f018bc80fa2e4b300a2e3","tid":2257532,"uid":149494,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:46:17.000Z","msg":"邊忽似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2f1788cf7dbfb39340de0c8580ae4c1c52ea1b","tid":2257532,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:48:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c37200ce39150d9e909844fe68a74c5e6ecd4bc6","tid":2257532,"uid":145273,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:52:59.000Z","msg":"咁東尼大木係咪都係私生子？"},{"pid":"8a46083ea2e75df4a3305f8c42f0cef5d5529f16","tid":2257532,"uid":137999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:58:28.000Z","msg":"問咗姐倫阿媽未"},{"pid":"e6c458cf715d5a072d85a38ac35f6172927d78d1","tid":2257532,"uid":21716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a46083ea2e75df4a3305f8c42f0cef5d5529f16","tid":2257532,"uid":137999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:58:28.000Z","msg":"問咗姐倫阿媽未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T09:17:48.000Z","msg":"問葉惠美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f2adead987e89d49ab8e0487ab1f1953648f273","tid":2257532,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T09:28:15.000Z","msg":"爸我回來了"},{"pid":"60eac879e5e74e0647331ddd2775e678de900b8c","tid":2257532,"uid":53666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T09:28:45.000Z","msg":"問過陳凱琳未"}]}